 First, you start with barak. You basically play a few creatures to hold you up and blast them with all the spells you can, and at the end of your turn, use prophecy to get some good cards.<br>
<br>
 Second, is Good ol ashgar. Dont forget to grab a krawg and boomstick when you get him because these cards are helpful. You play krawg right away and attack like heck cause u get to draw 2 cards plus he isnt effected by effects which is always nice. And when your opponent plays and annoyingly strong creature, balst it down with boom stick which is always fun cause it makes your opponent mad =) And dont forget those brushfires cause you can play one from your discards once a turn. And ashgars effect is good too but make sure you dont waste all the energy on spells and relics!<br>
<br>
 Last, is gar. Use him with creatures because of his nice effect. HE is good with lava balamant and magma jile. I dont have any lava balamants right now but im gunna add some. And keep your creatures strong in the line and use some of those spells like fireball and brush fire to light them on FIRE!<br>
